@startuml Clean Architecture Layers
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam roundcorner 10

title Clean Architecture - Fafi Dashboard

package "Presentation Layer\n(React)" #E3F2FD {
    [Pages] as pages
    [Hooks] as hooks
    [Components] as components
}

package "Domain Layer\n(Business Logic)" #FFF3E0 {
    [Entities] as entities
    [Use Cases] as usecases
    [Repository Interfaces] as interfaces
}

package "Infrastructure Layer\n(External Services)" #E8F5E9 {
    [Repository Adapters] as adapters
    [Repositories] as repos
    [External Services\n(Firebase)] as external
}

pages --> hooks : uses
hooks --> usecases : calls
usecases --> entities : creates
usecases --> interfaces : depends on
adapters ..|> interfaces : implements
adapters --> repos : delegates to
repos --> external : connects to

note right of hooks
  **Presentation Hooks:**
  - useProjects
  - useOrgs
  - useSales
  - useLocations
  - useSchedules
  - useStockAssets
  - useStockBalances
  - useProducts
  - usePremiums
  - useSettings
  - useACLs
end note

note right of usecases
  **Use Cases:**
  - List, Create, Update, Delete
  - Business logic orchestration
  - Entity validation
  - Repository coordination
end note

note right of entities
  **Domain Entities:**
  - Project, Org, Sale
  - Location, Schedule
  - StockAsset, StockBalance
  - Product, Premium
  - Setting, ACLRule
  - Pure business objects
  - No external dependencies
end note

note right of adapters
  **Dependency Inversion:**
  - Domain defines interfaces
  - Infrastructure implements them
  - Allows easy testing
  - Enables swapping implementations
end note

@enduml

